                            </a>
                        </div>

                        <div class="mt-4 md:mt-0 lg:flex lg:justify-end px-4 md:px-0">
                            <div class="flex md:gap-x-6 justify-between md:justify-end items-center flex-wrap md:h-10 gap-y-2">
                                <a href="#" class="text-xs md:text-base font-semibold text-white">Home</a>
                                <a href="#factalite" class="text-xs md:text-base font-semibold text-white">Factalite</a>
                                <a href="#howWeWork" class="text-xs md:text-base font-semibold text-white">How we
                                    work?</a>
                                <a href="#whoAreWe" class="text-xs md:text-base font-semibold text-white">Who are
                                    we?</a>
                                <a role="button" onclick="launchWhatsAppSignup()"
                                   class="hidden md:block bg-cyan-600 hover:bg-cyan-800 text-white text-xs font-bold py-1 md:px-3 rounded-full">
                                    Embedded signup
                                </a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </nav>
                </header>

                {# Chatbot title #}
                <div class="md:px-12">

                    <div class="mt-12 space-y-6 justify-center px-4 md:px-0 md:justify-between text-white md:flex flex-row md:gap-6 md:space-y-0 lg:gap-12 lg:items-center z-10">
                        <div class="md:w-2/3 lg:w-1/2">
                            <span role="heading"
                                  class="tracking-wide text-5xl leading-none font-bold text-white md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl"
                            >Privacy</span>

                            <p class="my-8 text-white text-xl">
                                This privacy policy is effective starting 1st of January, 2023 and has been written to
                                explain what data we collect, how we use it, and your rights as a user. This is in line
                                with the European General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR).
                            </p>

                            <div class="prose prose-lg container mx-auto px-4">
                                <h3 class="font-semibold mt-6 mb-4 text-xl mt-5 mb-2">1. Company Details</h3>
                                <p class="mb-3">Data Controller: Botalite SL</p>
                                <p class="mb-3">Address: Avenida del Manzanares 196 Local 2, 28026 Madrid.</p>

                                <h3 class="font-semibold mt-6 mb-4 text-xl mt-5 mb-2">2. What Data We Collect</h3>
                                <p class="mb-3">We collect data that you provide directly to us. This can include:</p>
                                <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-5">
                                    <li>Personal identifiers, contacts, and characteristics (for example, name and contact
                                        details)
                                    </li>
                                    <li>Any other information that you might provide voluntarily</li>
                                </ul>

                                <h3 class="font-semibold mt-6 mb-4 text-xl mt-5 mb-2">3. How We Use Your Data</h3>
                                <p class="mb-3">Your data will be used based on the following lawful grounds under the GDPR:</p>
                                <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-5">
                                    <li><strong class="font-semibold">Legitimate Interests:</strong> We use personal data as necessary for our
                                        legitimate interests. This includes getting back in touch with you once you provide
                                        us with your contact information or complete the Embedded Signup process so Botalite
                                        can provide services.
                                    </li>
                                    <li><strong class="font-semibold">Statistics:</strong> We may use anonymized data, from which any personally
                                        identifiable information has been removed, for statistical analysis to help us
                                        understand user behavior and trends, improve our service, and optimize our user
                                        experience.
                                    </li>
                                </ul>

                                <h3 class="font-semibold mt-6 mb-4 text-xl mt-5 mb-2">4. Sharing and Disclosure</h3>
                                <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-5">
                                    <li>If you submit data using Meta's Embedded Signup process, please be informed that
                                        your data will be treated according to Meta's privacy policy. We recommend you read
                                        their policy to understand their practices.
                                    </li>
                                    <li>Except as described above, we do not share, sell, rent, or trade any of your
                                        information with third parties without your consent.
                                    </li>
                                </ul>

                                <h3 class="font-semibold mt-6 mb-4 text-xl mt-5 mb-2">5. Data Retention</h3>
                                <p class="mb-3">We will retain your personal data only for as long as is necessary to fulfill the
                                    purposes for which it was collected and processed, including for the purposes of
                                    satisfying any legal, regulatory, accounting, or reporting requirements.</p>

                                <h3 class="font-semibold mt-6 mb-4 text-xl mt-5 mb-2">6. Your Rights</h3>
                                <p class="mb-3">Under GDPR, you have several rights regarding your personal data:</p>
                                <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-5">
                                    <li><strong class="font-semibold">Right to Access:</strong> You have the right to request access to your
                                        personal data that we hold.
                                    </li>
                                    <li><strong class="font-semibold">Right to Rectification:</strong> You can ask to have incorrect data
                                        corrected.
                                    </li>
                                    <li><strong class="font-semibold">Right to Erasure (‘Right to be Forgotten’):</strong> Under certain
                                        conditions, you can request your personal data to be erased.
                                    </li>
                                    <li><strong class="font-semibold">Right to Restriction of Processing:</strong> You can ask to restrict the
                                        processing of your data.
                                    </li>
                                    <li><strong class="font-semibold">Right to Data Portability:</strong> You can ask for your data to be
                                        transferred to another service provider.
                                    </li>
                                    <li><strong class="font-semibold">Right to Object:</strong> You can object to the processing of your data in
                                        some circumstances.
                                    </li>
                                </ul>
                                <p class="mb-3">To exercise any of these rights, please contact us.</p>

                                <h3 class="font-semibold mt-6 mb-4 text-xl mt-5 mb-2">7. Security</h3>
                                <p class="mb-3">We take appropriate security measures to prevent unauthorized access, disclosure,
                                    modification, or unauthorized destruction of the Data.</p>

                                <h3 class="font-semibold mt-6 mb-4 text-xl mt-5 mb-2">8. Changes to this Policy</h3>
                                <p class="mb-3">We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this
                                    page with an updated revision date. We encourage you to review this policy periodically
                                    for any changes.</p>

                                <h3 class="font-semibold mt-6 mb-4 text-xl mt-5 mb-2">9. How to Contact Us</h3>
                                <p class="mb-3">If you have any questions, comments, or concerns about this Privacy Policy or the data
                                    practices of Botalite SL, please address them to:</p>
                                <p class="mb-3">Botalite SL<br>
                                    Avenida del Manzanares 196 Local 2,<br>
                                    28024 Madrid<br>
                                    Spain<br>
                                    or using the contact e-mail address</p>
                            </div>

                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </section>
